name: MotherGooseNurseryRhymes
0:
”Alexa, start Mother Goose”
”Alexa, ask Mother Goose for "Baa Baa Black Sheep"”
”Alexa, ask Mother Goose for a rhyme about the itsy bitsy spider”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: mother goose
des: This skill gives you random nursery rhymes. You can also ask for a rhyme by title. Included are children's classics such as Jack and Jill, Humpty Dumpty, and This Little Piggy.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
